# Figma Concept Generation — Asio Neon + Widget Sizing Rule

## When This Rule Applies

Apply this rule whenever you are:
- Generating a UI concept (`ui/concepts/*.html`) from a feature description or PRD
- Building or annotating a widget layout that should conform to the Widgets-Templates-Library grid
- Referencing or hardcoding any color, type, spacing, or sizing value in a concept file

