## Typography Scale

Font family: **Inter** (load from Google Fonts or assume available).

| Token | Size | Weight | Line Height | CSS Class Name |
|-------|------|--------|-------------|----------------|
| `Headings/Light/H2` | 48px | 300 | 100% | `.h2-light` |
| `Headings/Light/H4` | 24px | 300 | 100% | `.h4-light` |
| `Headings/Bold/H4` | 24px | 700 | 100% | `.h4-bold` |
| `Text/16-Semibold` | 16px | 600 | 22px | `.text-16-semibold` |
| `Text/14-semibold` | 14px | 600 | 18px | `.text-14-semibold` |

Define these as CSS classes in every concept:

```css
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');

body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: var(--text-primary); background: var(--background); }

.h2-light    { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; }
.h4-light    { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; }
.h4-bold     { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; }
.text-16-semibold { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 22px; }
.text-14-semibold { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 18px; }
```

