## Concept Generation Template

Every new concept file in `ui/concepts/` must:

1. Start with the CSS variables block above
2. Declare the correct Google Fonts import
3. Define a widget container with `data-widget-size` and `data-framework` attributes
4. Use only token values — no hardcoded colors outside the `:root` block
5. Include a comment header identifying the concept, framework, and size tier

```html
<!-- 
  Concept: [Feature Name]
  Framework: [Datagrid | Timeline | Summary | Form | Insight]
  Size: [XXS | XS | S | M | L | XL | XXL]
  Size Rationale: [One sentence explaining why this size fits the content and use case]
  Source: [PRD URL or description]
  Generated: [YYYY-MM-DD]
  Figma Libraries: Asio Neon (a1eKyRtlUCKWmryjQPA4Q2), UXTT-Widgets (6gHlNEUBGcVMC7NJSlffXG)
-->
```

